{
  "stem": "17135.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 269.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- you know, they-- they constantly were fighting lice, because the-- the sanitary conditions were-- were impossible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they-- they give us underwear once every three months, you know, so you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and it was unavoidable that people got sick and there were-- there-- there were-- there was a typhus epidemic, where-- where-- where hundreds died from lice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a disinfection plant where the clothes were disinfected-- our clothes-- and when people came, they took away their civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were also disinfected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were stored in the magazine, or they were sent to German, to Germany, for-- for Germans to be used.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They sent us all to disinfection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we got very suspicious that they might-- and-- and, as I said, then there were rumors already that gas chambers are being built.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not in Sachsenhausen, but there are other concentration camps where they have gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The rumors were spreading.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Where they came from-- as I said, the political people in the inside had access to-- to-- to-- to radio.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And even SS men sometimes, in their stupidity, told them what was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- they gained their confidence by manipulating those people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The prisoners that were there-- were-- there were in Sachsenhausen 60 members-- former members-- of the German parliament.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were all highly educated people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were socialists and communists.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were professors, they were doctors, they were intellectuals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They somehow man-- worked also in the offices of the SS.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They used slave labor to do office function, that normally women do, like writing letters, filing, cleaning, what have you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And through their contact with those people, they got information that normally was not supposed to be available.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and we heard rumors.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
